==Talking to the Mysterious Stranger after getting Ranis' head==
* '''Mysterious Stranger:''' You again. What can I do for you?
* {{topt|I managed to recover Ranis' head.}}
** '''Player:''' I managed to recover Ranis' head.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Good work. Hand it over.
** {{tcond|If the player lost the head:}}
*** '''Player:''' Well... I seem to have lost it.
*** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' You should probably go and find it again then.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tbox|pic=Ranis' head detail.png|You give Ranis' head to the Mysterious Stranger.}}
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Hmm... Yes, I think this will work.
** '''Player:''' So what now?
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' It seems that Ranis has many memories of these eggs, or at least of something very similar. Thanks to my abilities, we can view these memories. Hopefully they will reveal the truth about Verzik.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Now, I suggest we start at the beginning. Take my hand.
** '''Player:''' Why are you making this weird?
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' I require physical contact to share the memory with you.
** '''Player:''' Oh... Fair enough.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Prepare yourself!
** {{qact|The first of Ranis' memories are displayed in the player's mind. Ranis Drakan, at [[The Maiden of Sugadinti]]'s chamber, is seen with a vyrewatch.}}
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' Do you have them?
** '''Vyrewatch:''' Right here, my lord.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' Excellent. I will take them from here.
** '''Vyrewatch:''' Of course.
** {{qact|Ranis Drakan walks towards Verzik Vitur.}}
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Ranis my dear, how wonderful to see you.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' And you Verzik.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' I see you've wasted no time in introducing our new guest to the Theatre.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' I must say, I find the name you've given her to be quite interesting. Not the kind of thing I'd have expected from you.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Well I thought it would be quite humorous.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' I see. So you intend to use her as a new challenge?
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' It seemed an ironically fitting role for her, given that fun little narrative you came up with. Besides, with all the work you put in, it would have felt wrong to just abandon her.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' You should not have worried about that. The things we learnt from her down in the labs more than made up for the effort.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Well either way, I'm glad she's here. I've found her to be quite the inspiration. Thanks to her, I've decided to give the whole place a bit of a sprucing up.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' You're replacing all the challenges?
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Absolutely! Those old ones were getting dull. It's time for some fresh excitement in this place.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' Well perhaps I have something that can help with that. I have a gift for you.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' A gift? Oh Ranis you do spoil me!
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' You can thank Lowerniel for this one. He found these eggs in an arachnid nest north of Darkmeyer. He thought you might be able to use them in your nylocas breeding program.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' How exciting! Do pass on my thanks. He is always welcome to come and pay me a visit himself, of course.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' The Theatre has never really been his thing.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Oh Ranis, I do love your brother, but he is such a bore! He needs to learn to live a little!
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Anyway, tell me more about this nest.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' The arachnids there are highly unique. Lowerniel thinks their queen might be of a higher power.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' A higher power? He doesn't think that silly stone he used to have is involved, does he?
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' No, he suspects something more natural.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Really? Well either way, if he's right, these eggs could be key to some very exciting new nylocas.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' I look forward to seeing the results.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' As do I...
** {{qact|The cutscene ends.}}
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Interesting... Very interesting...
** '''Player:''' That was Verzik?
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' It was. However, the memory was from many years ago, before she gained her unique abilities.
** '''Player:''' I see. So what's our next step?
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' The eggs in that memory were very similar to the ones in my possession, but they were not identical. It sounded like Verzik intended to use them to breed new nylocas.
** '''Player:''' Perhaps that breeding is what led to the eggs you have.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' And perhaps it was also the starting point for Verzik's abilities.
** '''Player:''' How can we be sure?
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' We will need to recover some of those eggs for ourselves. With them, we may be able to find further relevant memories.
** '''Player:''' Ranis said they came from a nest north of Darkmeyer. I'll see if I can find it.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Good idea. I will remain here.
** '''Player:''' Any reason why you're not able to join me?
** '''Player:''' Actually, let me guess. Your associates...
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' My associates would prefer I remain here.
** '''Player:''' I'm not sure why I asked. I'll be back once I've explored this nest.
