==Talking to the Mysterious Stranger after getting the eggs==
* '''Mysterious Stranger:''' You again. What can I do for you?
* {{topt|I found some of those eggs.}}
** '''Player:''' I found some of those eggs.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Excellent. Let's have a look at them.
** {{tcond|If the player lost the eggs:}}
*** '''Player:''' I don't actually have them with me.
*** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Well I'll need you to bring them here. They could be key to understanding Verzik's abilities.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tbox|pic=Strange spider eggs detail.png|You give the strange spider eggs to the Mysterious Stranger.}}
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Hmm... How curious...
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' I believe I can use these new eggs to help us find more memories of note. Hopefully they will start to present a clearer picture for us.
** '''Player:''' Well that would be nice. I'm still a bit lost to be honest... Then again, I guess that's just the norm for me.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Once we're done, I'll also have the eggs sent to my associates. Assuming they do have a connection to Verzik's abilities, they will come in very useful.
** '''Player:''' Your associates aren't trying to replicate her powers are they?
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Oh quite the opposite. Their hope is to find a way to counteract them.
** '''Player:''' Interesting...
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Anyway, I think I have found a new memory for us.
** '''Player:''' Let's take a look.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Prepare yourself!
** {{qact|Ranis' second memory is viewed. Ranis, alongside Verzik, meet in the Pestilent Bloat's chamber.}}
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' Bloat? Not the most elaborate of names, is it?
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' A crude name for a crude creation.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' Well it's most definitely crude... Quite disgusting as well.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Turns your stomach, does it Ranis? I'm surprised you'd find anything disgusting after what you did to that girl.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' I just think it's important to take a bit of pride in your work. This is a Theatre, Verzik. We should be producing art!
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Ranis darling, I couldn't agree more. Come have a look at this.
** {{qact|Ranis and Verzik walk towards a Nylocas Athanatos.}}
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' A new nylocas?
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' The athanatos! Isn't it magnificent!
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' It's quite a sight to behold.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' I have you and Lowerniel to thank for this one. This is the result of those eggs you gave me.
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' I'm glad you were able to make good use of them.
** '''Verzik Vitur:''' Oh I've been able to work wonders with them, and I'm not done yet. If all goes well, the athanatos will be just the beginning...
** {{qact|The cutscene ends.}}
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' So Verzik did manage to use those eggs to create new nylocas. However, something is still missing.
** '''Player:''' Is there another memory that could tell us more?
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Yes, I believe there is. Let us see what it can tell us.
** '''Mysterious Stranger:''' Prepare yourself!
** {{qact|Ranis' third memory is viewed. Ranis, alongside Verzik, meet in the nylocas chamber.}}
** '''Ranis Drakan:''' My my... You've really outdone yourself this time.
